pageProduct.name: Swisse Skincare Manuka Honey Daily Glow Foaming Cleanser 120ml
pageProduct.description:
General Information

With Vitamin C and Papaya Enzymes

Rise and shine with Swisse Manuka Honey Daily Glow Foaming Cleanser featuring stabilised Vitamin C and Papaya Enzymes. This refreshing and radiance-boosting cleanser delivers intense moisutre and a gentle clean for soft, dewy and glowing skin

Suitable For: Normal Skin

Size: 120mL

Warnings

This product contains essential oils. Test prior to use. In the unlikely event of a negative reaction, consult your medical practitioner.

Ingredients

AQUA (Water)
Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate
Sodium Lauroyl Sarcosinate
Cocamidopropyl Betaine
MANUKA HONEY Honey (Mel)
Xanthan Gum
Cananga Odorata Flower Oil
Citrus Nobilis (Mandarin Orange) Peel Oil
Juniperus Virginiana Wood Oil
Althaea Officinalis Root Extract
Banksia Serrata Flower Extract
PAPAYA (Papain)
Sodium Ascorbyl Phosphate
Citric Acid
Sodium Citrate
Benzyl Alcohol
Dehydroacetic Acid
98.9% naturally derived ingredients

Directions

Blend a small amount between palms and massage into wet skin in a circular motion. Rinse with warm water. Use twice daily, in the morning and evening.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store upright below 28°C.
